title: Creator Core w/ artists Joshua Citarella & Rachel Rossin (NM51)
itunes:author: New Models
itunes:summary:
Artists JOSHUA CITARELLA & RACHEL ROSSIN join NM for a freestyle audit of the 2022 art ecosystem. We discuss how the economy of cultural production, both on-platform and off, is evolving post peak-lockdown.

Originally released to NM subscribers 23 SEPT 2022

For more: https://rossin.co/ 
IG: @rachelrossin & @joshuacitarella 
https://patreon.com/joshuacitarella  
https://joshuacitarella.substack.com

Joshua Citarella, along with New Models, and Interdependence (Mat Dryhurst & Holly Herndon), is part of the channel.xyz network.
